Bumblebee/Injector/Manterror/Ramhorn/Counter Punch:



Bumblebee twirled through the air as shots hit him, slamminginto a tree.  One 
of his missile launchers fell from his hand.  Raising the other, he fired two 
stinger missiles at Striker.

---

Counter Punch charged in, tripping over a root that was underground, though 
partially above ground but covered by dirt.  Slamming down to the ground, his 
chin hitting a rock, he was a little dazed, but still raised his rifle, 
firing three bolts off at Ramulus.

---

Manterror and Injector approached from the behind the Maximals.

"Le-" Manterror was interrupted as Ramhorn sent a right hook to the Predacons 
face, knocking him to the ground.  Injector quickly kicked Ramhorn in the 
front of the knee joint.  As Ramhorn yelled in pain and fell, Injector fired 
a stinger missile into his chest.

---
